<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.9.9">
<l>nālvakai vēta maintu vēḷviyā ṟaṅkam vallār</l>
<l>mēlaivā ṉavariṉ mikka vētiya rāti kālam</l>
<l>cēlukaḷ vayalti ruppērc ceṅkaṇmā lōṭum vāḻvār</l>
<l>cīlamā tavattar cintai yāḷiyeṉ cintai yāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one in my mind is the ruler of the minds</l>
<l rend="indent">of those of great, virtuous penance,</l>
<l>Of those skilled in the four divisions of the Vedas, the five sacrifices,</l>
<l rend="indent">and the six branches [of knowledge],</l>
<l>Of those who dwell with bright-eyed Māl in Tiruppēr, where carp frolic</l>
<l rend="indent">in the paddy fields,</l>
<l>[Where] from the beginning of time, [dwell] brahmins</l>
<l rend="indent">who surpass the celestials above.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
